sections.heading: arrest; disobeying order; violation; penalty
sections.text: Any person who fails or refuses to obey any lawful order of a carrier enforcement officer or who resists lawful arrest by any such officer shall be deemed guilty of a Class III misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1955, c. 145, ยง 9, p. 408;Laws 1977, LB 39, ยง 92;Laws 1
